{"tid":667342,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"win10一打機就會爆ping","createTime":"2018-05-16T16:04:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T16:04:57.000Z","uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fe0ad20fc0f62d5e160152c1d18afad9d57c2ebf","tid":667342,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T16:04:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/16/235248_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F235248_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=93a9177b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n試過用電話同電腦同一時間ping返去隻router到<br />\n冇開game嗰陣個電腦ping係正常，但一開game就爆ping，關game又正常返<br />\n而電話個ping數就由頭到尾都正常(&lt;20ms)<br />\n啱啱發現如果display card usage比較高(e.g. 50%)嘅話電腦就會爆ping，究竟係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我用緊隻usb wifi adapter係tplink wn725n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nmb:asrock ab350m pro4<br />\ndisplay card:gigabyte gtx1060<br />\ncpu:ryzen 5 1600"}]}